results.name: Numbers n such that A136677(n) is prime.
link: Eric Weisstein, The World of Mathematics: Harmonic Number
mathematica: Do[ f=Numerator[ Sum[ (-1)^(k+1)*1/k^6, {k,1,n} ] ]; If[ PrimeQ[f], Print[ {n,f} ] ], {n,1,130} ]
